| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3581 — Recovery Inhibition (underground)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4fb2fb9a-31ee-50b1-8e56-e3d008f29f2c"
